I mean if you claim you can enjoy an 'adult activity' be responsible about it ne? Arg I hate people who are irresponsible about what they do; they give it a bad name for people who do it the right way. I mean you never hear of the responsible adults drinking on the news; just the fuck ups who have ten thousand beers and crash into a tree. People make things bad and corrupt; and the media only feeds on the bad because we are a taboo nation. In Europe sex, drugs, nudity are all exposed really.
